MERCURIES LIFE said unconsolidated sales
in March fell 2.10% to NT$10,541,517,000 from NT$10,768,102,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  3/2011           3/2010
Sales           10,541,517       10,768,102  
YOY%              -2.10%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           31,033,727       36,819,672  
YOY%             -15.71% 
=================================================================
 